item.title: OMNICODE
item.description: UNIX Quick Reference FILE rm -r #delete dir rm -f # force remove file cp -r dir1 dir2 # copy 1 to 2 creating dir2 if inexist ln -s file link # create symbolic link link to file Process killall proc # kill all processes named proc * bg # lists stopped or background jobs; fg a # brings job a to foreground File Permissions chmod octal file change permissions of file to octal,
